      %li= link_to 'Do I need to sign in to buy merchandise?', '#merchandise'

  .medium-8.columns
    %dl
      %dt#security Is my information secure?
      %dd
        %p
          %strong Yes.
          The Member Portal uses SSL to connect with your browser, which means the information you share with us is securely
          encrypted. In addition,
          %em we do not store any of your financial information on our servers.
          Instead, your information is passed on to
          = succeed ',' do
            = link_to 'Stripe', 'https://stripe.com', target: '_blank'
          a secure payment provider that manages credit cards and hands us a token by which to connect your account to their
          data. The only retrievable information Stripe maintains is the last four digits and expiration of your card, for
          your own reference, and tokens by which we can securely make charges. You will receive a receipt from us and from
          Stripe for every transaction.
      %dt#signup How do I become a member?
      %dd
        %p
          Simple! Just go to the #{link_to 'home page', root_path} and click "Sign Up." Once you've created an account,
          you can purchase a membership in one quick step. That’s it! Once you’ve done that, you’re a Midnight Rider, and
          you’ll have access to all of the benefits of being one, including Supporters Lot parking, merchandise discounts,
          and full access to the Member Portal.
      %dt#username I'm already a member. What's my username?
      %dd
        %p
          If you signed up in person at a Riders event this year or last, you were sent a welcome email with your login
          information around the time you signed up. If you’re not the
          %em primary accountholder
          of a Family membership, you do not have an account yet.
          %strong= link_to 'See below', '#relatives'
          for more information about family members.
          The
          %strong default username
          is your first name and last name with no capital letters and no spaces. For example,
          Jay Heaps would be
          = succeed '.' do
            %strong jayheaps
      %dt#password What’s my password?
      %dd
        %p
          If you signed up in person at a Riders event this year or last, you were sent a welcome email with your login
          information. If you know you have an account but don't remember your password,
          %strong= link_to 'click here', new_user_password_path
          to request a password reset email. If you’ve never logged in,
      %dt#relatives Can family members have their own logins?
      %dd
        %p
          Not
          %em right now.
          We are currently developing the capability for those with Family memberships to add and administer User accounts
          for qualifying family members. Stay tuned!
      %dt#merchandise Do I need to sign in to buy merchandise?
      %dd
        %p
          Not at this time. Just visit #{link_to 'the shop page', 'http://midnightriders.com/shop', target: '_blank'} to
          get all your Riders merch.
